,"column":7},"end":{"row":12,"column":573},"action":"remove","lines":["Daniel runs his own music studio offering private lessons for piano and violin called Appassionato Music Studio. He currently teaches over 25 students of various experience levels from age 4 to adults. Daniel has co-founded the Apostle Island trio, who gave their debut performance at the Steinway & Sons store in Madison on January 2017. He gives solo and chamber performances throughout the year and has taken leadership roles in multiple musical events in the Madison area. As a leader, he is a co-chair of the Madison Area Music Educators (MAME) Honors Festival."],"id":39},{"start":{"row":12,"column":7},"end":{"row":12,"column":199},"action":"insert","lines":["Daniel has performed recitals in multiple venues locally, nationally and internationally. His most notable performance venues are Carnegie Hall in New York and Musikverein in Vienna, Austria. "]}],[{"start":{"row":14,"column":7},"end":{"row":14,"column":122},"action":"remove","lines":["Outside of music, Daniel enjoys role playing and video games, spending time with family, and training in Taekwondo."],"id":40},{"start":{"row":14,"column":7},"end":{"row":14,"column":563},"action":"insert","lines":["Daniel runs his own music studio offering private lessons for piano and violin called Appassionato Music Studio. He currently teaches students of various experience levels ages 4 through adults. Daniel has co-founded the Apostle Island trio, who gave their debut performance in 2017. He gives solo and chamber performances throughout the year and has taken leadership roles in multiple musical events in the Madison area. As a leader, he is a co-chair of the Madison Area Music Educators (MAME) Honors Festival and the former treasurer of the organization."]}],[{"start":{"row":16,"column":7},"end":{"row":16,"column":112},"action":"remove","lines":["Daniel looks forward to educating, inspiring and sharing music with the community for many years to come."],